title: Ranks?No, thanks. Go play normals!

embed.description: Hey guys Im Bleachy, 22 years old, and an unprofessional Gamer! Here is my third video. I was totally pissed of by the ranksystem and the mood of every player. :D GO FOR NORMALS! If you like it, pls subscribe and click the like-button! More important is that u share it!

body:
Hey guys
Im Bleachy, 22 years old, and an unprofessional Gamer!
Here is my third video.
Figured out that the mood in ranked games is not like it should be. Everyone is just aiming for the game, and not for fun...
I was totally pissed of by the ranksystem and the mood of every player. :D GO FOR NORMALS!
If you like it, pls subscribe and click the like-button!
More important is that u share it!
Its a new channel and i need every help i can get.
Thanks.
